Record Class Inventory

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
db.Inventory
Record Components:
uniqueId - The unique identifier of the inventory item.
unitCost - The cost per unit of the inventory item.
amountOnHand - The current amount of the inventory item in stock.
amountNeeded - The amount of the inventory item needed.
amountOrdered - The amount of the inventory item that has been ordered.
description - A description of the inventory item.
public record Inventory(int uniqueId, double unitCost, int amountOnHand, int amountNeeded, int amountOrdered, String description) extends Record
A record representing an inventory item with various attributes such as cost, amount on hand, and description.
